column5: Does anyone know if this program is still on for 2009?  I submitted a few fish in 2008 and had an account established.  When you go to the site the 2008 stuff is still there, but the site is still active.  I submitted a fish anyways but was just wondering if anybody knew for sure.  Thanks Jim
Yes...  it's still on for 2009. Members here have been submitting their  OFC tourney entries since January for extra inches in our tourney.
Goin for the Gold this year are ya Jim
Just want to put some 2009 stickers on the new boat Joey !!
